OL,3,CMan cleared over masked group's 'show
OL,4,Cof strength'
OL,6,FLoyalist Stephen Matthews has been
OL,7,Fcleared of being part of a masked mob
OL,8,Finvolved in an alleged 'show of
OL,9,Fstrength' in east Belfast four years
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,FThe 62-year-old was cleared on charges
OL,13,Fof unlawful assembly, affray and
OL,14,Fintimidation dating back to February
OL,15,F2021.
OL,17,FCo-accused Derek George Lammey was
OL,18,Facquitted on unlawful assembly and
OL,19,Faffray charges but was found guilty of
OL,20,Fan intimidation offence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
