OL,3,CMan cleared over masked group's 'show
OL,4,Cof strength'
OL,6,FThe 60-year-old was told by Judge
OL,7,FGordon Kerr KC that he will be
OL,8,Fsentenced on May 29.
OL,10,FThe judgment followed a non-jury trial
OL,11,Fheld at Belfast Crown Court in April.
OL,13,FDuring the hearing, the Crown made the
OL,14,Fcase that both men were involved in an
OL,15,Fincident in the Pitt Park/Fraser Pass
OL,16,Farea of east Belfast.
OL,18,FBoth Mr Matthew from Meadow Park in
OL,19,FBallywalter and Lammey of Hill Crest
OL,20,Fin Bangor denied all three charges
OL,21,Flevelled against them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
