OL,3,CMan cleared over masked group's 'show
OL,4,Cof strength'
OL,6,FAs well as refusing to answer
OL,7,Fquestions during police interviews
OL,8,Ffollowing their arrests, both men
OL,9,Fdeclined to give evidence at trial.
OL,11,FIt was the Crown's case that both were
OL,12,Fpart of a "threatening and
OL,13,Fintimidating group" of around 40
OL,14,Fmasked and hooded men who gathered in
OL,15,FPitt Park before walking to the
OL,16,FBallymac Centre which was occupied by
OL,17,Fwoman and children.
OL,19,FThose inside the centre included the
OL,20,Fwife and daughter of murdered man Ian
OL,21,FOgle.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
