OL,6,FThe crowd gathered outside the centre
OL,7,Ffor a short period and some comments
OL,8,Fwere directed to those inside before
OL,9,Fthe group dispersed.
OL,11,FAs he gave his judgment, Judge Kerr
OL,12,Fspoke of the evidence presented at the
OL,13,Ftrial.
OL,15,FRegarding cell site analysis which
OL,16,Fplaced both men in the area at the
OL,17,Frelevant time, the Judge deemed this
OL,18,Fas 'neutral' as in February 2021, both
OL,19,Fmen were living in the area.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
