OL,6,FJudge Kerr also branded as 'neutral'
OL,7,Fthe evidence regarding clothing.
OL,9,FThis included suggestions that Mr
OL,10,FMatthews was pictured prior to the
OL,11,Fincident wearing a coat similar to the
OL,12,Fone worn by the male in the crowd in
OL,13,FPitt Park which the Crown alleged was
OL,14,FMr Matthews.
OL,16,FTurning to Mr Matthews first, Judge
OL,17,FKerr noted that the "primary evidence"
OL,18,Fagainst him was identification by two
OL,19,Fpolice officers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
