OL,6,FAt this point Judge Kerr told Mr
OL,7,FMatthews he could leave the dock.
OL,9,FHe then turned to the evidence against
OL,10,FLammey and concluded that in his view
OL,11,Fthe accused was part of the masked
OL,12,Fgroup.
OL,14,FThis, the Judge said, was based partly
OL,15,Fon the voice recognition.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
