OL,3,CMan cleared over masked group's 'show
OL,4,Cof strength'
OL,6,F"Accordingly, I find the defendant not
OL,7,Fguilty on count one", he said.
OL,9,FRegarding the affray charge, the Judge
OL,10,Fsaid this was an allegation that in
OL,11,Fthe vicinity of Pitt Park/Fraser Pass,
OL,12,FLammey unlawfully displayed force and
OL,13,Fmade an affray.
OL,15,FHe said: "I'm not persuaded that the
OL,16,Fbehaviour of the crown constituted a
OL,17,Fdisplay of force, as is required for
OL,18,Fthe offence, nor was there actual
OL,19,Fviolence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
