OL,6,F"I am not sure or firmly convinced
OL,7,Fthat the relevant elements required to
OL,8,Fbe convicted of affray have been
OL,9,Festablished so I find the defendant
OL,10,Fnot guilty of that offence."
OL,12,FConcerning the intimidation charge,
OL,13,Fthis alleged that Lammey unlawfully
OL,14,Fcaused by force, threats or menaces
OL,15,Fpersons within the Ballymacarett
OL,16,FCentre to refrain from returning to
OL,17,Ftheir place of residence.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
