OL,3,CMan cleared over masked group's 'show
OL,4,Cof strength'
OL,6,FJudge Kerr spoke of the "movement of
OL,7,Fthe crowd" as they made their way to
OL,8,Fthe centre, the shouts directed at
OL,9,Fthose inside and the fear which Ms
OL,10,FJohnston spoke about.
OL,12,FHe said that these features, coupled
OL,13,Fwith the way the men were masked and
OL,14,Fthe way they moved in a "co-ordinated
OL,15,Ffashion" towards the centre, indicated
OL,16,Fthe "clear intention" of the group -
OL,17,Fwhich included Lammey - was to
OL,18,F"intimidate those inside the centre
OL,19,Fand keep them there."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
