OL,3,CMan cleared over masked group's 'show
OL,4,Cof strength'
OL,6,FBranding this as a "show of strength",
OL,7,FJudge Kerr said he was "firmly
OL,8,Fconvinced" of Lammey's guilt and
OL,9,Fconvicted him on the charge of
OL,10,Fintimidation.
OL,12,FHe confirmed he would sentence Lammey
OL,13,Fon May 29 and agreed to release him on
OL,14,Fcontinuing bail.
OL,16,FSpeaking after Mr Matthews was
OL,17,Facquitted on all charges, Darragh
OL,18,FMackin of Phoenix Law revealed
OL,19,Fconsideration is now being given to
OL,20,Fcivil proceedings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
