OL,6,FMr Mackin said: "This acquittal marks
OL,7,Fan important vindication for our
OL,8,Fclient. We will now be examining all
OL,9,Flegal avenues available, in light of
OL,10,Fwhat we believe to have been an
OL,11,Funjustified and damaging prosecution."
OL,13,FThe solicitor added that the outcome
OL,14,Fof the case has raised wider questions
OL,15,Fabout the use of identification
OL,16,Fevidence in prosecutions relating to
OL,17,Fpublic protests.
